data.description: Sitting in the heart of Pace and convenient to everything!  Nice brick home with huge shop and several outbuildings.  There is also room to garden and already has fruit trees in place.  Three bedroom open floor plan with an additional bonus room that has a separate entrance that could be used for an extra bedroom (no closet) or den.  Go out from the dining room and you have the perfect craft, paint or sewing room (12x17) in it's own private little area.  Out back you will find garden sheds and storage including a 28x32 garage with power.  Roof is 3 years old, HVAC has been recently serviced, new water heater. Bull nose corners and spanish lace walls were original upgrades. 8 foot privacy fenced back yard.
